# ══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
# Sovereign Agent Lab — Environment Variables
# ══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
#
# HOW TO USE THIS FILE
# ────────────────────
# 1. Copy this file:   cp .env.example .env
# 2. Open .env and replace every placeholder with your real key.
# 3. Never commit .env — it is in .gitignore for a reason.
#
# RULES FOR ALL KEYS
# ──────────────────
# • No quotes around values:    NEBIUS_KEY=sk-abc123     ✓
#                               NEBIUS_KEY="sk-abc123"   ✗
# • No spaces around the =:     NEBIUS_KEY=sk-abc123     ✓
#                               NEBIUS_KEY = sk-abc123   ✗
# • If a key is not needed yet, leave the placeholder — don't delete the line.
#
# ══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
# WEEK 1–5 — Required from day one
# ══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

# Nebius Token Factory — your primary LLM API key.
# Used for every model call throughout the entire course:
# Llama 3.3 70B, DeepSeek R1, Kimi K2, Qwen3, FLUX image generation.
# Get yours at: https://studio.nebius.ai → API Keys
NEBIUS_KEY=sk-your-key-here

# ══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
# WEEK 2 — Tools & MCP (web search)
# ══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

# Tavily — web search API used by the research agent in Week 2.
# Free tier: 1,000 searches/month. Sign up at: https://tavily.com
# Leave blank if not yet on Week 2.
TAVILY_API_KEY=tvly-your-key-here

# ══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
# WEEK 4 — RAG & Memory
# ══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

# Pinecone — vector database for the RAG pipeline in Week 4.
# Free tier: 1 index, 100k vectors. Sign up at: https://pinecone.io
# Leave blank if not yet on Week 4.
PINECONE_API_KEY=pcsk-your-key-here
PINECONE_INDEX_NAME=sovereign-agent

# ══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
# WEEK 5 — Production & Observability
# ══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

# LangSmith — tracing and observability for LangGraph agents.
# Free tier available. Sign up at: https://smith.langchain.com
# Leave blank if not yet on Week 5.
LANGSMITH_API_KEY=lsv2-your-key-here
LANGSMITH_PROJECT=sovereign-agent-lab
# Set to "true" to enable tracing, "false" to disable.
LANGCHAIN_TRACING_V2=false

# ══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
# TRACK B ONLY — Rasa Digital Employee (voice pipeline, Weeks 3–5)
# ══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

# Speechmatics — speech-to-text (ASR) and text-to-speech (TTS).
# Used in the voice pipeline: microphone → Speechmatics → Rasa → Speechmatics → speaker.
# Sign up at: https://speechmatics.com → API Access
# Leave blank if you are on Track A, or not yet building the voice pipeline.
SPEECHMATICS_API_KEY=your-speechmatics-key-here

# Rasa Pro licence — required only if you upgrade from open-source Rasa
# to Rasa Pro for advanced CALM features and the voice pipeline.
# Your instructor will provide this if it is needed for your track.
# Leave blank if you are using open-source Rasa (the default for Week 1–2).
RASA_PRO_LICENSE=your-licence-key-here